			<creator>Lipps Inc.</creator>
			<album>How long (Ace)</album>
			<trackNum>1</trackNum>
			<annotation>The origins of this song go a lot deeper than I expected. The song was originally a 1974 song by the artist Ace, which had a Polish cover in 1980 by Lipps Inc.. It wasn&#39;t until 2020 that it was inserted over a GIF of a dancing cow, spawning the Polish cow meme.</annotation>
